18:T401,This is a modular polyethylene insert component for the Latitud Triad dual mobility hip system, not a standalone implant class. It is a component that works within a larger dual mobility construct (metal liner + polyethylene insert + femoral head). The brochure clearly describes it as HXLPE-90KGY material with gamma sterilization, designed for dual bearing surface articulation with 22mm and 28mm head compatibility. However, critical information is missing: (1) no brand confirmation - 'Meril Life Sciences' is listed as manufacturer but brand field is empty; (2) no external verification available; (3) size range and exact liner compatibility specifications are not documented. The entity_type is 'instrument' (component) rather than 'implant_class' because this is a replaceable modular component, not the primary implant. Review required to: confirm brand ownership, verify this is indeed part of Meril's Latitud product line, and obtain complete technical specifications including size range and compatibility matrix.7:["$","div",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-[#0A0A0A] text-white","children":[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org/\",\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"Latitud Triad Dual Mobility Modular Polyethylene Insert\",\"description\":\"Highly cross-linked polyethylene insert (HXLPE-90KGY) for dual mobility hip system. Designed to work with metal liner and femoral head assembly for enhanced hip stability and reduced wear.\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"Meril\"},\"category\":\"Hip Acetabular Components\",\"manufacturer\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Meril Life Sciences\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateOffer\",\"offerCount\":\"1\",\"lowPrice\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"INR\",\"availability\":\"https://schema.org/InStock\"}}"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-24","children":[["$","nav",null,{"className":"